<h5>Description</h5>
<h2 style="text-align: center;" data-mce-style="text-align: center;">Smart Coffee Table Classic | Futuristic Furniture</h2>
<p>This Steinfield Tech Smart Coffee Table Classic is designed to enhance the enjoyment and the usage of the same amount of space in your living room. With two refrigerator drawers, USB ports, fast wireless charging. It is not simply a furniture item, this Smart Coffee Table will elevate your living room.</p>
<p>The Built-in refrigerator 90L drawer holds beer, soda, wine, and more for any occasion. USB ports and fast wireless charging to keep your devices charged by your side without having to leave the conversation or in the middle of a movie. A LED touch control panel is built-in seamlessly into the tempered glass top, easy to access the volume and adjust the temperature of the refrigerator drawer. It is the perfect item for any home.</p>
