<h5>Key Features</h5>
<h3>Stay Charged</h3>
<p>USB charging ports and wireless charging to keep your devices charged by your side without having to leave the conversation or in the middle of a movie.</p>
<h3>Stay Chill</h3>
<p>The built-in 90L refrigerator with two separate drawers holds beer, soda, wine, and more. Individual temperature control lets you keep fresh fruits or snacks at the ideal temperature. <span data-mce-fragment="1">Adjustable Refrigerator Temperature Range: 37-54 Degrees Fahrenheit</span>.</p>
<h3>Smart interface</h3>
<p>A LED touch control panel is built-in seamlessly into the tempered glass top, easy to access.</p>
<h3>Tempered Glass Top</h3>
<p>The round-safe edge design on the corners and the strong and scratch-resistant tempered glass top are perfect for anything you put on top.</p>
<h3>Energy Efficient</h3>
<p>Low noise at 40dB running seamlessly in the background and 24h a day with only 0.41Kwh. </p>
